description: It was cold and windy this day. And I started the hunting quite late. Three, four boys have been rather reluctant when I tried to even start a conversation. But then I saw this tall blonde leaving a small shop next to a tram station. He was open minded. At least I thought so. We talked about his job, his salary. He was quite interested in making some extra money. But when I came closer to the point and started to ask him to show me his dick his attitude suddenly changed. He seemed aggressive but nonetheless the offer seemed somehow tempting to him. Once he made the first step it took me some time and a lot of money to make him follow me into the hotel. But then... wow, what a performance^^
title: Czech Hunter 76
